{"tid":1681251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麥巴比去利物浦？名宿：曼聯更適合","createTime":"2019-10-29T09:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T09:34:22.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d02a42d5e73c5876921b025c9c31df2ffd98b3d8","tid":1681251,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:49:48.000Z","msg":"《每日鏡報》報導，前美國國腳、曾在富咸效力過的前鋒麥拜特近日接受《ESPN》採訪時表示，他不建議麥巴比（Kylian Mbappe）去利物浦，而曼聯或許能成為麥巴比生涯的一大挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n  「利物浦是家偉大的球會，但你期待他全場壓迫嗎？你想讓他在場上像紅軍三叉戟那樣參與防守嗎？我並不認為你希望他這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n  「而巴塞和皇馬，誰不想在美斯（Lionel Messi）身邊踢球？皇馬現在有些下滑，不過，如果你真的想擔起一支球隊並給它帶來質變，那曼聯就是個不錯的選擇。」"},{"pid":"2dc8e284777426ef7579663b9922f4faef05c5a5","tid":1681251,"uid":247019,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"以為奧雲講"},{"pid":"216dd34de3110e511627d299d09308e9770ad627","tid":1681251,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯就是個不錯的選擇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb13333347b7e4c2c6e52dbff012494be44b4f9","tid":1681251,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"邊銀個"},{"pid":"63159a86c86e0ba8be49f79afac684482ad3aa76","tid":1681251,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"明叔，邊撚個明叔呀，睇過睇過屌你老屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79efb8c8e9e1a60db8825b02af7fb7491f737e87","tid":1681251,"uid":111006,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"去猁隊波應該勁撚到仆街，佢又咁撚快，啱晒高普"},{"pid":"bf44a9132113c90faf395c61f7ec26f335de330f","tid":1681251,"uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"216dd34de311